article.description: — Jeremy Sheppard tied his career high with a season-high 25 points as Rhode Island romped past Milwaukee 82-58 on Monday night.
article.headline: Sheppard lifts Rhode Island over Milwaukee 82-58
article.linkText: Sheppard lifts Rhode Island over Milwaukee 82-58
article.story: MILWAUKEE -- — Jeremy Sheppard tied his career high with a season-high 25 points as Rhode Island romped past Milwaukee 82-58 on Monday night. Makhi Mitchell had 16 points for Rhode Island (8-3). Milwaukee scored 21 first-half points, a season low for the team. DeAndre Gholston had 16 points for the Panthers (2-8). Donovan Newby added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
